xt/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1edd t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ph\u00eda n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 12/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n do ph\u00eda n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o l\u1ecbch t\u1eadp l\u00fac 18h00 \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u00fac 20h00.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BHL \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1edfi n\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ea3o l\u1ed9n gi\u1edd gi\u1ea5c \u0103n u\u1ed1ng, ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Do \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng Park \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh hu\u1ef7 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u1edf s\u00e2n xi m\u0103ng g\u1ea7n kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n Harper Lippo Cikarang.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ong Duong Vu Lam cho rang quy trinh dinh chi cong tac cua VFF khong dung\" title=\"\u00d4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m cho r\u1eb1ng quy tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a VFF kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2013/6/duong-vu-lam-1370863894_500x0-201361022301.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m ngao ng\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao. Nh\u01b0ng khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y l\u1ecbch v\u00e0 l\u00ean xe chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea5y 5 ph\u00fat th\u00ec BTC b\u00e1o ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp, ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1edd xu\u1ed1ng 20 gi\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i gi\u1eefa \u1ee6y ban Olympic v\u00e0 Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, l\u1ecbch t\u1eadp \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00fac 18 gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p v\u00ec n\u1eb1m trong khu v\u1ef1c qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5y ph\u00e9p t\u1eeb BTC m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed5i xu\u1ed1ng 20 gi\u1edd v\u00e0 s\u00e2n t\u1eadp kh\u00e1c, s\u00e2n Babik c\u00e1ch s\u00e2n t\u1eadp d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn 20 ph\u00fat n\u1eefa. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh hu\u1ef7 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp \u1edf tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00ea t\u00f4ng, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m\u00a0cho bi\u1ebft do c\u00e1c s\u00e2n c\u1ecf \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c xung quanh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00ean ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng cho c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3\u00a0tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h ng\u00e0y 14/8 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft l\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tinh th\u1ea7n. V\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-tiep-tuc-bi-nuoc-chu-nha-indonesia-gay-kho-de-168-194336.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/olympic-viet-nam-tiep-tuc-bi-nuoc-chu-nha-indonesia-gay-kho-de.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-tiep-tuc-bi-nuoc-chu-nha-indonesia-gay-kho-de-168-194336.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 do b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc-168-194334.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc-168-194334.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5407","checkdouble":"194341"},{"date":"21:59 12/08","title":"Sevilla 1-2 Barca: Messi v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/sevilla-vs-barca-sieu-cup-tbn-2018-dem-nay.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng song m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, Blaugrana \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y t\u00ednh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd m\u00e0 HLV Valverde \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng khi \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Pique v\u00e0 Dembele \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</h2><h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: SEVILLA 1-2 BARCA\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/13/Sevilla-vs-Barcelona.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\nBarca thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a H\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua. T\u1ea1i  International Champions Cup 2018, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 h\u00f2a 1 v\u00e0 thua 2 sau 3  tr\u1eadn. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n n\u00e0y, Barca \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng trong s\u1ed1 18 \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1  ICC n\u0103m nay. Tuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1edfi h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5  c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalunya kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 ICC 2018 do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i th\u00eam sau  VCK World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga th\u00ec tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Barca trong  m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Sevilla. Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi n\u0103m, m\u00e0n  th\u01b0 h\u00f9ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi 1 tr\u1eadn duy nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u1edf Morocco (nh\u1eefng  n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e1 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00e0 v\u1ec1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t T\u00e2y Ban Nha).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, Barca mua s\u1eafm kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh tay khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Nou Camp m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t  t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arturo Vidal, Arthur Melo, Malcom v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0  Clement Lenglet - trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Sevilla \u1edf  m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Vidal ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c &ldquo;th\u1eed l\u1eeda&rdquo; trong lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn  \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ICC 2018, c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3 Arthur  l\u1eabn Malcom \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n &ldquo;m\u1edf t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n&rdquo; trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Barca.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Sevilla vs Barca tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Sevilla vs Barca tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Truc-tiep-Sevilla-vs-Barca-tran-dau-Sieu-cup-TBN-2018-dem-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Messi v\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Barca trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111o\u1ea1t c\u00fap \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y kh\u00ed th\u1ebf v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a  gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, HLV Valverde \u01b0u ti\u00ean cho c\u00e1c &ldquo;ma c\u0169&rdquo; ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t  quen thu\u1ed9c t\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn Sevilla run r\u1ea9y nh\u01b0 Luis Suarez, Sergio Busquets, Jordi  Alba v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ea1i si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch  xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN c\u0169ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho v\u00e0i t\u00e2n  binh.</p>\r\n<p>C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Lenglet c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Pigue \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a Umtiti  ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, t\u00e2n binh Arthur Melo s\u1ebd l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i, ph\u00e2n  ph\u00e1t b\u00f3ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Xavi hay Iniesta, hai huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t t\u1eed c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Tuy  nhi\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c, Malcom th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh  s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n Coutinho d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb khi m\u00e0 sao tr\u1ebb Dembele \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean  h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Messi vs Suarez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSevilla c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN khi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ea1ch 4 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n  th\u1eafng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i Champions League. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0  \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng nh\u01b0 trung v\u1ec7 Joris Gragnon (15  tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Rennes), ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ibrahim Amadou (15 tri\u1ec7u euro, Lille), th\u1ee7  m\u00f4n Tomas Vaclik (7 tri\u1ec7u euro, Basel) v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Aleix Vidal -  ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Sanchez Pizjuan t\u1eeb ... Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 8,5 tri\u1ec7u euro. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau l\u1ea7n  gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha duy nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2007, Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3  th\u00eam 2 l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2010 v\u00e0 2016. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3: \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9  Andalucia \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 k\u1ebb h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c h\u1ecd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Barca.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sevilla\" title=\"Sevilla\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/4F0CCB7800000578-6052945-image-a-18_1534108601157.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sevilla v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 \u01b0u th\u1ebf s\u1edbm r\u01a1i v\u00e0o tay  Barca. Tuy v\u1eady, g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalunya t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 t\u1eeb t\u1ed1n, ru ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng  ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e0o \u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1nh ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed5 ra \u1edf ph\u00fat  th\u1ee9 9. Sevilla t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhanh v\u00e0 Luis Muriel \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho  Sarabia tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i x\u1eed l\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng trong ch\u00e2n trai,  \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 g\u00f3c xa trong s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Stegen. Ph\u1ea3i sau m\u1ed9t h\u1ed3i li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi  \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 VAR (tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i video), tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn  b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean n\u00f3 h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 100%. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n, Barca d\u0129 nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 &quot;b\u00ecnh ch\u00e2n nh\u01b0 v\u1ea1i&quot; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa m\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft  \u0111\u1ea7u ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea9y cao nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00f2ng ki\u1ebfm  b\u00e0n g\u1ee1. S\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u n\u1ed5i l\u00ean b\u00ean c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Sevilla v\u00e0 c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 t\u0103ng d\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec1u theo  th\u1eddi gian. Tuy v\u1eady, sau h\u01a1n n\u1eeda hi\u1ec7p 1, Barca h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i  nguy hi\u1ec3m n\u00e0o d\u00f9 b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn l\u0103n b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sevilla.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 28, t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi, trung v\u1ec7 Lenglet l\u00ean tham gia su\u00fdt  ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi CLB c\u0169. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfm hoi m\u00e0 Barca  c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Sevilla cho \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1 nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c  b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbcc gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao. Ph\u00fat 42, Lionel Messi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t  chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, b\u00f3ng xuy\u00ean qua h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o ch\u1eafn nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i  \u0111\u1eadp c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc b\u1eadt ra. Trung v\u1ec7 Pique c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 xo\u1ea1c ch\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o  l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng. C\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn x\u00e1c minh v\u1edbi t\u1ed5 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd tr\u1ecdng  t\u00e0i video th\u00ec \u00f4ng vua s\u00e2n c\u1ecf m\u1edbi c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"pique\" title=\"pique\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/4F0CE3B200000578-6052945-image-a-19_1534108727532.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Trung v\u1ec7 Pique g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Barca sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t tr\u00fang c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, Sevilla ch\u00fat n\u1eefa l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn b\u00e0n n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Stegen  kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 qu\u00e1 hay \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Muriel. Sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9  gi\u1ea3i lao, HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 khi ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Ivan Rakitic  \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay th\u1ebf Rafinha, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 g\u1eafn m\u00e1c La Masia v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n  trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 song khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nh\u1ea1t  nh\u00f2a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSo v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p 1, Barca kh\u00f4ng kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n bao nhi\u00eau, bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 54  tu\u1ed5i&nbsp; ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a th\u00eam ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng Coutinho v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay Melo, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c  \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u01b0 Rafinha. Ph\u00fat 60, nhi\u1ec1u  C\u0110V Barca l\u1ea1i kh\u1ea5p kh\u1edfi m\u1eebng th\u1ea7m khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1  ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Lionel Messi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n  n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Vaclik \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ee9u nguy th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho Sevilla.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0i ph\u00fat sau, t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Banega, Vazquez ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 ch\u1ecdn \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i r\u1ed3i  th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o m\u00e9p tr\u00ean x\u00e0 ngang.  Barcelona mau ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 khi Messi m\u1edbm b\u00f3ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho Dembele nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n  \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1997 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Sevilla. Sau s\u1ef1  c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Rakitic v\u00e0 Coutinho, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc. \u00c1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean  khung th\u00e0nh CLB x\u1ee9 Andalusia t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dembele\" title=\"Dembele\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/4F0D105300000578-6052945-image-a-25_1534110676983.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sao tr\u1ebb Dembele ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 78, Blaugrana \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Sau khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Vaclik  ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp hai pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga (1  trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Messi),&nbsp; Ousmane Dembele nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh Messi, d\u1eabn  v\u00e0i nh\u1ecbp r\u1ed3i tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Sevilla t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u1ea1ch 16m50. Th\u1eddi  gian kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 Sevilla bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00ean t\u1ea5n  c\u00f4ng h\u00f2ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Barca c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p co c\u1ee5m \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0  &quot;l\u1ea5y t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u00e0m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1&quot; thi \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1i gia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ecbch t\u00ednh t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i cho  Sevilla h\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n v\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Stegen \u0111\u00e3 truy c\u1ea3n tr\u00e1i ph\u00e9p Vidal,  c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ecm ngh\u1ec9m \u1edf Camp Nou sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ed3i n\u0103m 2015 v\u00e0  vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Sevilla ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n  c\u1ee7a Wissam Ben Yedder l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n n\u00ean b\u1ecb Stegen b\u1eaft v\u1ecb th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1eady l\u00e0, Barca \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Sevilla \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN&nbsp;th\u1ee9 13 v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a CLB. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 nh\u01b0 \u00fd cho La Liga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nSevilla:</strong> Vaclik; Gomez, Kjaer, Mesa, Mercado (Wissam Ben Yedder 85'), Escudero, Sarabia (Aleix Vidal 71'), Banega, Navas,  Muriel (Andre Silva 60'), Vazquez.<br>\r\n<strong>Barcelona:</strong> Ter Stegen; Alba, Pique, Lenglet, Semedo; Rafinha (Rakitic 46'), Busquets, Arthur  Melo (Coutinho 53'); Dembele (Arturo Vidal 86'), Luis Suarez, Messi.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Sevilla 1-2 Barca\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Sevilla 1-2 Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/13/Thong-so-Sevilla.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Sevilla 1-2 Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong>C\u00f4ng Minh (TTVN) </strong></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5406","checkdouble":"194340"},{"date":"05:48 13/08","title":"V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau C\u00fap, Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/13/vo-dich-sieu-cup-lionel-messi-lap-ky-luc-moi-trong-mau-ao-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sevilla, Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 danh hi\u1ec7u gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barcelona v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam m\u1ed9t Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0o b\u1ed9 s\u01b0u t\u1eadp.</h2><h2>Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n, Barca \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 ban \u0111\u1ea7u khi gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla v\u1edbi m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Ousmane Dembele l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng cho Barca.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi lap ky luc ve so danh hieu gianh duoc trong mau ao Barca\" title=\"Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 danh hi\u1ec7u gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/vo-dich-sieu-cup-lionel-messi-lap-ky-luc-moi-trong-mau-ao-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 danh hi\u1ec7u gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng Messi l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t. Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2018 gi\u00fap Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Barcelona.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Leo&quot; t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu 33 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Andres Iniesta v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 32 danh hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Vissel Kobe (Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u00e0 s\u01b0u t\u1eadp danh hi\u1ec7u<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 33 danh hi\u1ec7u gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f9ng Barca, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau C\u00fap th\u1ee9 8 c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi. Ngo\u00e0i ra, &quot;Leo&quot; \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 9 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga, gi\u00e0nh C\u00fap nh\u00e0 vua t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 7 l\u1ea7n, b\u1ed1n l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, 3 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 Club World Cup c\u00f9ng v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2009, 2011 v\u00e0 2015.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Messi \u0111\u00e3 5 l\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 5 l\u1ea7n, Messi \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f9ng Barcelona.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Messi, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c &quot;th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 1987&quot; c\u1ee7a Barca l\u00e0 Gerard Pique v\u00e0 Sergio Busquets khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 28 danh hi\u1ec7u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia. Xavi Hernandez, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn nh\u1ea5t cho Barca c\u0169ng c\u00f3 25 danh hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra \u0111i v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-sevilla-12-barca-sieu-cup-tbn-2018-328-194358.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/video-tong-hop-sevilla-12-barca-sieu-cup-tbn-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-sevilla-12-barca-sieu-cup-tbn-2018-328-194358.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Sevilla 1-2 Barca (Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN 2018)</span><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng song m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, Blaugrana \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y t\u00ednh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 tri\u1ebft...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/sevilla-vs-barca-sieu-cup-tbn-2018-dem-nay-372-194340.html\">Sevilla 1-2 Barca: Messi v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-sevilla-vs-barca-3h-ngay-138-co-messi-la-co-tat-ca-180-194294.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 13/8): C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-108-messi-chinh-thuc-tro-thanh-tan-doi-truong-barca-184-194199.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 10/8: Messi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/cuoc-chien-ronaldo-vs-messi-nong-lan-sang-ca-khoan-du-thuyen-188-193849.html\">Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn Ronaldo vs Messi n\u00f3ng lan sang c\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n ... du thuy\u1ec1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tro-thanh-dong-doi-messi-vidal-len-tieng-cam-on-hum-xam-180-193716.html\">Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Messi, Vidal l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n H\u00f9m x\u00e1m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/thu-mon-barcelona-tham-vong-qua-mat-ca-messi-180-192583.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Barcelona tham v\u1ecdng qua m\u1eb7t c\u1ea3 Messi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5405","checkdouble":"194357"},{"date":"01:45 13/08","title":"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u00f9i d\u1eadp West Ham 4 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/3-ly-do-giup-liverpool-vui-dap-west-ham-4-ban-khong-go.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-0. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y r\u1eaby t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1edbi The Kop. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Klopp gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</h2><h2>B\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1eabn gi\u1eef phong \u0111\u1ed9\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u00f9i d\u1eadp West Ham 4 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u00f9i d\u1eadp West Ham 4 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/James-Milner-khen-ngoi-Naby-Keita-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>B\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Salah, Mane v\u00e0 Firmino c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool</span> v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. H\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha di chuy\u1ec3n lu\u1ed3n sau l\u01b0ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 West Ham v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb k\u00e9o kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Declan Rice trong nhi\u1ec1u pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady m\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMichail Antonio li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecf qua nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng l\u1ed7 h\u1ed5ng l\u1edbn b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang ph\u1ea3i. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady m\u00e0 Andy Robertson c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ed9i bom t\u1eeb v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 Salah m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a West Ham c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 ng\u1ee7 \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Mane sau pha c\u0103ng ngang c\u1ee7a Milner cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. L\u1ed7i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a &ldquo;B\u00faa t\u1ea1&rdquo; c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 n\u00e9t trong hai b\u00e0n thua sau \u0111\u00f3 khi h\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 Mane c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Salah tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi West Ham v\u1eeba qua ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 West Ham kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap cho The Kop d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0103n \u00fd\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool vs West Ham\" title=\"Liverpool vs West Ham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb West Ham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Liverpool th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd thi tho\u1ea3ng b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 b\u1ecb thua nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi West Ham t\u1ea1i Anfield cho th\u1ea5y hai tuy\u1ebfn n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ra sao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 Alexander-Arnold, Joe Gomez, Van Dijk v\u00e0 Robertson ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Wijnaldum, Milner v\u00e0 Naby Keita \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n m\u1ecdi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a West Ham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWijnaldum \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. Anh c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n l\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. Anh \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1edbi 92% \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. Nh\u01b0ng Wijnaldum v\u1eabn n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nMilner g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 h\u01a1n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Naby Keita c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a The Kop c\u0169ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u01a1 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Joe Gomez v\u00e0 Van Dijk c\u0169ng k\u1ec1m t\u1ecfa t\u1ed1t Arnautovic v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c1o g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, vi\u1ec7c tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Liverpool ch\u01a1i \u0103n \u00fd h\u01a1n \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng West Ham g\u00e2y nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/james-milner-khen-ngoi-naby-keita-172-194344.html\">Ra m\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f3 ng\u1ee3i ca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sadio-mane-sau-tran-thang-west-ham-liverpool-chua-muon-dung-lai-172-194342.html\">Sadio Mane sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng West Ham: Liverpool ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Naby Keita ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 hay\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Naby Keita\" title=\"Naby Keita\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Naby Keita ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng Naby Keita v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t nh\u1ea5t trong ng\u00e0y ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Anfield. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Leipzig cho th\u1ea5y h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00f4i khi v\u1eabn b\u1ecb ch\u00ea l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n an to\u00e0n nh\u01b0 chuy\u1ec1n sang hai h\u00e0nh lang bi\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng khi c\u00f3 Keita, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Guinea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng x\u1ed9c th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee1 n\u00e0o v\u00e0 g\u00e2y ra nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e2m th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Keita \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho Robertson b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 tung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Salah trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKeita c\u0169ng thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng, ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 t\u00ec \u0111\u00e8 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Liverpool chuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1eeb th\u1ee7 sang c\u00f4ng nhanh v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Mane, Keita li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 West Ham v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u00e2y x\u1ea9m m\u1eb7t m\u00e0y su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u1eeba qua l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i sao Keita l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady. Qua th\u1eddi gian, khi \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec3u m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League h\u01a1n, Keita ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Keita qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Liverpool vs West Ham:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278984\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/12/liverpool-westham-1534084348.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5404","checkdouble":"194348"},{"date":"02:03 13/08","title":"Cech: \"Tr\u1eadn thua Man City gi\u00fap Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Petr Cech tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates v\u1eeba qua.</h2><h2>Arsenal thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Raheem Sterling v\u00e0 Bernardo Silva \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Unai Emery.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng pressing ngay t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Man City. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i test nh\u01b0 Man City l\u00fac n\u00e0y qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Arsenal.</div>\r\n<h2>Cech \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Cech c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Petr Cech \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh sau tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua th\u00eam v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u00edt h\u01a1n. Trong hi\u1ec7p hai, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong kh\u00e2u tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong 1/3 s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m pha b\u00f3ng. Khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin nh\u01b0 Man City th\u00ec m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u00ecn chung, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 th\u1eadt t\u1ec7 khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra trong hi\u1ec7p hai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV m\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh nhanh h\u01a1n\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVideo t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City:<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278994\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/13/arsenal-mancity-.mp4&autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-arsenal-02-man-city-172-194347.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-arsenal-vs-man-city-02-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194346.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Arsenal 0-2 Man City (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5403","checkdouble":"194349"},{"date":"02:34 13/08","title":"Sterling l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng khi\u00eau kh\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/sterling-ly-giai-man-an-mung-khieu-khich-o-tran-gap-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Raheem Sterling t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Sterling g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Arsenal v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-0 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf Premier League. V\u00e0 Sterling \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p b\u00e0n khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t pha solo tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung c\u00fa s\u00fat xa h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Petr Cech.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed1i l\u1eadp ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Sterling t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Khi \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng g\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Sterling h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ebft th\u00fac b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng khi\u00eau kh\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sterling l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng khi\u00eau kh\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/sterling-ly-giai-man-an-mung-khieu-khich-o-tran-gap-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sterling \u0103n m\u1eebng khi\u00eau kh\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Sterling \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t 1 tay l\u00ean tai \u00fd mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch anh gi\u1edd \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u. V\u00e0 trong b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c \u0103n m\u1eebng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u00f4i n\u00ean t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c \u0103n m\u1eebng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. B\u1edfi v\u00ec t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u1edfi s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00ecnh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bernardo Silva vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Bernardo Silva l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-0 cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ph\u00fat 64. V\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a The Citizens.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Arsenal l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon-172-194349.html\">Cech: Tr\u1eadn thua Man City gi\u00fap Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-arsenal-02-man-city-172-194347.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5402","checkdouble":"194350"},{"date":"03:59 13/08","title":"C\u1ef1u sao M.U n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/gary-neville-noi-ve-tran-arsenal-02-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi Sky Sports, c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean CLB M.U, Gary Neville \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn HLV Unai Emery c\u1ea7n 3, 4 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00f3a s\u1ea1ch \u2018di s\u1ea3n\u2019 m\u00e0 HLV Wenger \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</h2><h2>Gary Neville n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Neville n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Neville n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/gary-neville-noi-ve-tran-arsenal-02-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gary Neville cho r\u1eb1ng Unai Emery c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i\u00a0</span>Arsenal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n k\u00e9m vui sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110KV\u0110 Man City ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n t\u1eeb xa y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 khi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Xhaka v\u00e0 Guendouzi kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Petr Cech ph\u1ea3i hai l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng sau nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat xa uy l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Man xanh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u sao M.U Gary Neville \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i tr\u00ean Sky Sports: \"T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Emery s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn ra \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ef3 qu\u00e1i m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi\u00a0Man xanh. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n. Emery s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n 3,4 m\u00f9a chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u00f4ng \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n nh\u01b0 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn\u201d. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, c\u1ef1u sao Arsenal Paul Merson l\u1ea1i nghi ng\u1edd vi\u1ec7c HLV Emery chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Stephan Lichtsteiner n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 34 tu\u1ed5i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cUnai \u0111\u00e3 mua nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Arsenal c\u1ea7n. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. <o:p></o:p>\u0110\u1ea5y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Lichtsteiner c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Arsenal, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7n 35 tu\u1ed5i... <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 bao nhi\u00eau c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u1edf Premier League? \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00f3? Tuy nhi\u00ean, Unai \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, r\u1ed3i m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian\u201d, Paul Merson chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n k\u00e9m vui tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Unai Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 s\u1ebd \u00edt c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Chelsea \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-arsenal-vs-man-city-02-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194346.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/clip-arsenal-vs-man-city-02-highlights-premier-league-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-arsenal-vs-man-city-02-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194346.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Arsenal 0-2 Man City (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19)</span><br>\r\nMan City ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5401","checkdouble":"194351"},{"date":"06:01 13/08","title":"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/13/5-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-thuyet-phuc-cua-man-city-truoc-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Arsenal, Man City \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2-0. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 0-2 Man City n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>1. Arsenal \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng&hellip;</h2>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i Emirates, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ea7y nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c cao. HLV Unai Emery ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u00e1p s\u00e1t nhanh, g\u1eaft v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Man City g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u00f4i qua, Man City ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n. H\u1ecd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng k\u00e9o gi\u00e3n ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Benjamin Mendy b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, Raheem Sterling c\u1eaft v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9, qua m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p l\u00e0m ng\u1ee1 ng\u00e0ng c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/5-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-thuyet-phuc-cua-Man-City-truoc-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Sterling \u0111\u00e1nh tan t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ai ng\u1edd Sterling l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tung c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 k\u1ef3 \u1ea3o t\u1edbi v\u1eady. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1nh c\u00f3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a Man City. Sau khi chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng cho Sterling, Mendy di chuy\u1ec3n nhanh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m k\u00e9o theo s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2y, Sterling r\u1ea5t nhanh c\u1eaft v\u00e0o trong v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 0-2 Man City. Trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Man City th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi v\u00e0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Bernardo Silva ph\u00fat 64.</div>\r\n<h2>2. Emery \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng</h2>\r\nV\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 Arsenal s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City l\u00e0 4-2-3-1. Tuy nhi\u00ean, do h\u1ecd l\u00f9i qu\u00e1 s\u00e2u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u00ean. B\u1ed9 ba ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Gabon bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i tham gia thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 qu\u00ean lu\u00f4n ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft cho anh.<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery\" title=\"HLV Emery\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/HLV-Emery.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery qu\u00e1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 0-2 Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea5t d\u00e0i l\u00ean cho Aubameyang c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng khi n\u00e0o \u0111\u00fang t\u1ea7m. B\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n \u0111i qu\u00e1 s\u00e2u khi\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 14 tr\u1edf n\u00ean hoang mang \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p. C\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Auba t\u1edbi t\u1eeb n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a anh v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111i thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSang hi\u1ec7p 2, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n t\u1eeb Arsenal. Ch\u00ednh \u00e1p l\u1ef1c pressing ngay ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Man City m\u1eafc m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 sai l\u1ea7m. Nh\u1eefng Alexandre Lacazette hay Mesut Ozil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i song \u00edt ra c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u0169ng g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Arsenal.</div>\r\n<h2>3. Man City kh\u00f4ng cho Arsenal l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Emery tin r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng n\u01a1i ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u1eadm r\u00e3i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Arsenal h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf r\u1ee7i ro tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1eeb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech cho t\u1edbi b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tho\u00e1t \u00e1p s\u00e1t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal vs Man City Bernardo Silva vs Xhaka\" title=\"Arsenal vs Man City Bernardo Silva vs Xhaka\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Arsenal-0-2-Man-City-Pep-Team-khong-ngu-quen-tren-chien-thang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Man City c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u00e1p s\u00e1t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Arsenal r\u1ea5t nhanh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed7i khi h\u1ecd c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. Qu\u1ea3 nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. Su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa, Cech \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &ldquo;t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3&rdquo; v\u1edbi pha x\u1eed l\u00fd h\u1edb h\u00eanh. N\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi, sai s\u00f3t n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd \u00e1m \u1ea3nh anh trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Cech c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i sai l\u1ea7m m\u00e0 Emery thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp. \u0110\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng Granit Xhaka hay Guendouzi c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 cho b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Man City.</div>\r\n<h2>4. HLV Guardiola \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh r\u1ea5t nhanh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00fat 54, HLV Emery quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00fat Aaron Ramsey v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o Alexandre Lacazette. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian m\u1edbi k\u1ecbp l\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Man City. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Ramsey, Emery c\u0169ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u1eb7p Lacazette v\u00e0 Aubameyang song h\u00e0nh trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pep Guardiola\" title=\"HLV Pep Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/HLV-Pep-Guardiola.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Guardiola cho th\u1ea5y nh\u00e3n quan chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. Lacazette gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng Aubameyang kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p s\u00e1t sao c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Man City. Anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tung c\u00fa vu\u1ed1t b\u00f3ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Arsenal ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ph\u00fat sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n song \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, Guardiola \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch tung Kevin De Bruyne thay Riyad Mahrez ngay c\u1ea3 khi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Algeria chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c. V\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2y, s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a De Bruyne \u0111\u00e3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y Man City. Ph\u00fat 64, Mendy c\u0103ng ngang v\u1eeba t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 Bernardo Silva x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m tung n\u00f3c l\u01b0\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n<h2>5. C\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh Arsenal c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Emery ra m\u1eaft Arsenal, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Stephan Lichtsteiner v\u00e0 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Guendouzi, Lucas Torreira. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 Sokratis. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kinh nghi\u1ec7m song ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c Mustafi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Guendouzi\" title=\"Guendouzi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/hlv-emery-benh-vuc-hoc-tro-sau-that-bai-truoc-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh nh\u01b0 Guendouzi c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLichtsteiner v\u00e0o thay Maitland-Niles ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t. Lichtsteiner l\u00e0m tr\u00f2n vai trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 pha c\u1eaft b\u00f3ng k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGuendouzi cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea7m nh\u1ecbp, \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 19, anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha b\u00f3ng non n\u1edbt v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin n\u01a1i c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Torreira \u1edf 20 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u1ecd bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 HLV Emery c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh l\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong ch\u1edbp m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Arsenal 0-2 Man City\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 0-2 Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Thong-so-Arsenal.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 0-2 Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 0-2 Man City (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278994\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/13/arsenal-mancity-.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/gary-neville-noi-ve-tran-arsenal-02-man-city-172-194351.html\">C\u1ef1u sao M.U n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sterling-ly-giai-man-an-mung-khieu-khich-o-tran-gap-arsenal-172-194350.html\">Sterling l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng khi\u00eau kh\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon-172-194349.html\">Cech: Tr\u1eadn thua Man City gi\u00fap Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-arsenal-02-man-city-172-194347.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5400","checkdouble":"194359"},{"date":"15:56 12/08","title":"Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/12/23/ronaldo-muon-juventus-mua-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic t\u1eeb Lazio, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Don Balon c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Lazio. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 to\u00e0n n\u0103ng, anh v\u1eeba ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea1i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua anh ghi 12 b\u00e0n \u1edf Serie A.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Cristiano-Ronaldo-muon-Juventus-mua-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m. MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic, Man City, Barca, Real hay PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Lazio, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 110 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ecf ra ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i. Barca, Real v\u00e0 PSG \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic t\u1eeb Lazio, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Don Balon c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/Cristiano-Ronaldo-muon-Juventus-mua-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic--hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Milinkovic-Savic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCR7 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia, anh mu\u1ed1n Juventus chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSi\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Serie A, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Milinkovic-Savic, b\u1edfi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Lazio y\u00eau c\u1ea7u l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 chi\u1ec1u l\u00f2ng CR7 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi chi 105 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ronaldol, s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Juventus ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia. Ngo\u00e0i Milinkovic-Savic, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus-176-194109.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Marcelo </span>c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, song th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5399","checkdouble":"194317"},{"date":"14:54 12/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam vs Mes Sungun Varzaghan 18h00 ng\u00e0y 12/8 (Futsal ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/link-xem-thai-son-nam-vs-mes-sungun-varzaghan-futsal-chau-a-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Link xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam vs Mes Sungun Varzaghan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam vs Mes Sungun Varzaghan chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i Futsal ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 c\u00e1c CLB l\u00fac 18h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 12/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<h2>LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnextin.vn%2Fvideos%2F2128474780760021%2F&amp;show_text=0&amp;width=560\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden\" scrolling=\"no\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"100%\" height=\"500\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> - Danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh: H\u1ed3 V\u0103n \u00dd, Roberto Tobe, Nguy\u1ec5n Minh Tr\u00ed, T\u00f4n Th\u1ea5t Phi, Al-Tawail.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/anh4.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<h2>Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam t\u1ea1o k\u1ef3 t\u00edch khi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i futsal ch\u00e2u \u00c1</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Bank of Beirut (Lebanon) d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-1 \u1edf hi\u1ec7p hai, Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 6-5 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i futsal c\u00e1c CLB ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i futsal c\u00e1c CLB ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nagoya Ocean - nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch futsal Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.\r\n<h2>HLV Miguel Rodrigo: 'T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam'</h2>\r\nThuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bank of Beirut (Lebanon) t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i futsal c\u00e1c CLB ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Miguel Rodrigo d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2: &quot;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c. C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 3-1. S\u1ef1 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nTh\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam 6-5 Beirut\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/10/Thai-Son-Nam-FC-6-5-Bank-of-Beirut.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5398","checkdouble":"194313"},{"date":"15:59 12/08","title":"Danh th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i AFF Cup 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/12/danh-thu-nhat-ban-se-doi-dau-tuyen-viet-nam-tai-aff-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Campuchia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Keisuke Honda v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean CLB Melbourne Victory n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u00f3i chung b\u1edfi l\u1ebd Keisuke Honda th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0a ra tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eeba \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho CLB Melbourne City \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia Australia sau k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Keisuke Honda l\u00e0m gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Campuchia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Keisuke Honda l\u00e0m gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Campuchia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/df.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Campuchia t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia. \u1ea2nh: CNCC.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Melbourne Victory l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng hay nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Australia. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng nhau, ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y bi\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u n\u00e0y gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a b\u1edfi theo CNCC, Keisuke Honda \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p HLV khi c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Melbourne Victory \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Honda kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh m\u00e0u \u00e1o m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Prak Sovannara \u0111ang t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi gi\u1eef v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Campuchia sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Leonardo Vitorino ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Keisuke Honda th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp CLB Melbourne Victory, Honda t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Mexico trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Pachuca. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 32, anh v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, khi \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Keisuke Honda l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1eebng chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. \u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 CSKA Moscow v\u00e0 AC Milan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Honda t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Campuchia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 AFF Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 11 t\u1edbi, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Zing.vn<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5397","checkdouble":"194319"}]}